Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(618,424)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  你们这群死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you braindead barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把蟹黄堡放下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,drop those patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.12,0:01:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们手上的三明治必须跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your sandwiches are coming with me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.56,0:01:12.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:12.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww, so cute
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想捏捏他的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to pinch his face
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.06,0:01:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这位宝贝小甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this precious, little sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱的脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those adorable cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.53,0:01:27.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好闪亮的大眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:27.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sparkly eye
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.80,0:01:28.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:28.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.19,0:01:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱的屁屁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That adorable tuchus
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.96,0:01:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.45,0:01:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.47,0:01:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨这座城
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate this town
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.83,0:01:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来猜猜看  又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, another failure?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, another failure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又要怎么偷到蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to steal the Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都把我当小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when everybody thinks I'm adorable?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱完全让人怕不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cute is no way to inspire fear
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.42,0:02:04.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:04.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.07,0:02:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要让全裤头村的白痴知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll teach the fools of this town
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.20,0:02:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱一样也能怕起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that cute can be horrific
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.75,0:02:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我的邪恶大作完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, my evil masterwork is complete
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一颗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An egg?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.10,0:02:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经吃过早餐了  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already had breakfast, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛋不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not the egg
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面的东西才重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's what's inside
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.49,0:02:28.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个阴险恶毒  心狠手辣的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:28.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A robot so diabolical, so devious
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.44,0:02:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还可爱到让人一看就会说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so adorable when people see it, they'll have to say
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Aww"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是那声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that sound
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会让它变形成一个可怕的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will transform it into a terrifying monster
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那些人都吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that will eat them
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,复仇机器人模型  小可派
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Revenge-bot model QT-Pi
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说它会吃人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say it was going to eat people?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.82,0:03:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被吃掉的人会被关进它的量子胃监狱里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Its victims will be trapped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in its quantum stomach prison
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.22,0:03:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反思自己的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,think about what they've done?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好好玩你的小玩具去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, have fun with your little toy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.10,0:03:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了拿垃圾出去倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget to take out the trash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.85,0:03:12.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:12.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It works
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.20,0:03:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:34.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,686)}海之霸专属财产
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.53,0:03:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1260,975)}真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1260,1030)}Barnacles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:34.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(488,800)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.25,0:03:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.45,0:03:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那白痴一定会对我机器人啊个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That moron won't be able to stop aww-ing at my robot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.35,0:03:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上啊  机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, robot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat him
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狠狠吃掉他  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat him good, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A --
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it comes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱护好你这个可爱小机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cute, little robot like you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能让你孤零零地自个在外头待着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,shouldn't be out here all alone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小可派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,QT-Pi?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.22,0:04:16.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一起找主人  顺便让我关照你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you until we find your owner
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我们打入敌人的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take us right into my enemy's lair
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这上班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where I work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.19,0:04:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些是我们的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are our customers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是章鱼哥  我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this is Squidward, my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好肮脏的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is a filthy lie
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说到肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speaking of filthy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.16,0:04:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得先洗把脏手再去做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better wash these dirty hands before I get cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  行行好帮我看好他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, be a dear and keep an eye on him for me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真是太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, you are pretty cute
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say cute?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.07,0:04:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.67,0:04:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's so cute
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往后稍稍  畜生们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get back, you animals
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.03,0:05:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他当宝贝也得给人家空间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He needs room to be precious
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.65,0:05:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面不像是大声哭诉自己被宰的喊声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those don't sound like "I'm spending money" screams
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.92,0:05:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好把手擦干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Proper drying of the hands
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重要程度堪比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is every bit as important as the--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wha--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来今天关门挺早的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess we closed early today
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就有不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I have more time
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以帮我新朋友小可派了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to help my new friend QT-Pi
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the name of Neptune is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.65,0:06:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, what is happening here?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.00,0:06:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  想必都是你干的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, this has you written all over it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别血口喷人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:14.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1074,630)}海之霸专属财产
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意是怎么挂上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd that get on there?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  都是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, it was me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为了教训你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To teach you all a lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就做了个机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.35,0:06:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,专门吃说了啊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that eats people who say, "aww"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快告我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So sue me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想告你  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to sue you, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要从你的地狱机关里逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to get out of your infernal contraption
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃出去的唯一出路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the only way out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是紧急疏散小舌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the emergency evacuation uvula
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而它就在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which is up there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1126,810)}紧急出口
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.80,0:06:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  听见小个子说的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you heard the pipsqueak
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家叠罗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone form up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉动小舌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's yank that "uvuler"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来想要逃出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're stuck here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.45,0:07:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得先等这破机器人多吃点人进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until this dumb robot eats more people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(922,468)}兽医
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兽医可以帮忙找到你主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The veterinarian can help me find your owner
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定就有身份芯片了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you must be chipped
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.42,0:07:26.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一般只治动物  不治机器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Normally I work with animals, not machines
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过又有啥区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but how different can they be?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来听诊一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just take a listen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, "Aww"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让它吃你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get eaten
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, "Aww"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay then, say "aww"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.72,0:07:42.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:42.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.08,0:07:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.79,0:07:57.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:57.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I meant to say
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So cute
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1172,570)}手套乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.75,0:08:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买票才能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to buy a ticket
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(556,730)}热狗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美  就往这边逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect, I'll escape through there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:07.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1406,396)}死胡同\N游乐设施
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死胡同游乐设施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dead end ride?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉跟手套主题不怎么搭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem very glove themed
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小可派  求你别吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,QT-Pi, please don't eat me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.04,0:09:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.81,0:09:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来使出音乐抚慰人心的神奇力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try the soothing power of music
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  该死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw, rats
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.01,0:09:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我准备的惊喜派对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A surprise party for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是派对  你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't a party, you boob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我一进来大家怎么都在欢呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why did everyone cheer when I showed up?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为有你在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because with you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.52,0:09:49.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就能够得到紧急逃生小舌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:49.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can finally reach the emergency escape "uvuler"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  大家再来叠罗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, let's try it again, people
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.50,0:10:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We escaped
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.97,0:10:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我让大家免费进手套乐园玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I got us into Glove World for free
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一个上碰碰手套的变臭鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Last one on the bumper gloves is a rotten egg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的小可派
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor QT-Pi
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃掉大家没法帮你解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That whole eating everyone thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,didn't work out for you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I know
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以怎样利用你的能力做好事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how you could use your powers for good
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1108,190)}手套发射场
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来试玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step right up and try
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.59,0:11:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们独具手套特色的全新游乐项目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our latest glove-tastic ride
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.14,0:11:11.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来手套发射场体验世界啊灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:11.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Experience the aww-pocalypse at the Glove Launch
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶耶耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我太矮不能玩是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean I'm too short to ride this ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(794,290)}世界啊末日求生成功\N准备好再来一轮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:38.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(524,362)}手套套提醒\N长这么高才能玩哦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我发明的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I built this
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,规矩就是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rules is rules
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这种可爱小不点也必须得遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even for an adorable little guy like you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.40,0:11:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Real cute
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.55,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FF97&\fs160\fsp50}邮递员派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(695.802,342)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(709.802,636)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:51.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(759.802,668)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(631.802,468)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(743.802,534)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(981.802,656)}联合监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(275.802,510)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
