Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,932)}邮件
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我新石头终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My new rock is finally here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圆点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,polka dots?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我订的可是纯色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ordered plaid
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.13,0:12:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得退回去  邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to take it back, Mr. Mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.69,0:12:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mailman?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My back
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You okay, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得把邮件送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotta deliver mail
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.97,0:12:36.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在什么东西都不适合去送
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:36.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are in no shape to deliver anything, fella
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松就好  来我家睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just relax and crash at my place
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天来帮你送邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll deliver your mail for you today
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘带邮包了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost forgot my mail bag
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘戴邮递员帽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost forgot my mailman hat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All righty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看我第一单往哪家送
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see where my first delivery is
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't read this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  一听就知道是你头在撞门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, I thought that sounded like your head
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, do you know where this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.53,0:13:19.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨绵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:19.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spon-gee-Boob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包包住哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squir-pa-Nants lives?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never heard of him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  退给寄件人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, return to sender
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么穿了新衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with the new threads?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是邮递员了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a mailman now
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都很想当邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to be a mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像每天都当圣诞老人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like getting to be Santa every day
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星期天例外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,except Sundays
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我才是邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm the mailman now
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.58,0:13:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你可以当我邮递伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you can be my postal pal
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起来送邮件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get mailing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.27,0:14:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮递伙伴  你来按门铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Postal pal, you may ring the doorbell
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.42,0:14:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮递员长官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mailman, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先给按门铃的手指热身一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better warm up the old bell ringer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上下上下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up, down, up, down
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,右边扭扭  左边扭扭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twist right, twist left
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再抹个指甲油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And polish the nail
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mail
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮局让你们俩白痴送邮件了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They let a moron like you deliver the mail?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.82,0:14:32.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮局让白痴做的事肯定会让你吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:32.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd be surprised what they let morons do
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到货了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到货了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥的脸怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Squidward's face?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好像在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think he's smiling
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.52,0:14:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于到手了  我的涡轮竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally got it, my turbo clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每分钱都值得花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worth every penny
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1336,460)}腌椰菜
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  下一站到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, good, our next stop
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,担任陪审团职务的传票
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A summons for jury duty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.27,0:15:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干的漂亮  邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great job, Mr. Mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这投信口一定有毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be a defective mail slot
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ought to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是按门铃试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just try the doorbell
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是跳过这家  送下一家的邮件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just move on to the next house
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮递誓词有言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like the postal oath says
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.22,0:16:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管是上刀山下火海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,neither bunions or onions nor ditches or dangers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.15,0:16:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都要把邮件送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will stop me from giving stuff to strangers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别给我递
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special un-delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.29,0:16:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当邮递员跟当圣诞老人就不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being a mailman isn't like being Santa Claus at all
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是胡须兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're beard bros
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱼诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Fishmas
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在七月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's July
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收封信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take a letter
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上刀山下火海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neither bunions or onions
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我收信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take your mail
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要狠狠编你码
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll zip your code so hard
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,En garde
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,En lard
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要贴你邮票
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stamp you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寄给你一套屁递
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll send you butt express
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你公民义务是逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't run from your civic duties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打我可以  退回不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,slap back, no take backs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这传票是海霸王的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This summons is for Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这俩白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you nincompoops
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.01,0:18:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't leave
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.90,0:18:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  从来没人来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I never get visitors
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.35,0:18:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寄给特别老人家的特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery for one special, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找不到寄给他的信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't find any mail for him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没收到信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never get any mail
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.47,0:18:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's so sad
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他送点别人的邮件  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's give him some of the other mail, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到寄给你的信了  助步器老头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found a letter for you, Old Man Walker
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,554)}助步器老头
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被征召了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been drafted
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1274,634)}取消赎回权
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么一封信能让他这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If one letter made him this happy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把所有邮件都给他一定会高兴到爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet all of the mail will make him explode with joy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是寄给我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all of this for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.95,0:19:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来要送到哪  邮递员派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's next, Postman Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮件都送光了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all out of mail
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去问问那辆冰淇淋车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's ask that ice cream truck
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看它知不知道要去哪找邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if it knows where to find some mail
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.41,0:19:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是冰淇淋车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's no ice cream truck
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是邮车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a mail truck
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为大卡车都是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought all trucks were girls
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开邮车中大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We hit the postal jackpot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.60,0:20:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那俩怪人偷了我邮车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those weirdos stole my truck
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.45,0:20:26.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快追那俩偷信贼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:26.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow those postal pilferers
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A special delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给弗雷德的特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery for Fred
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是卡罗尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's Carol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,684)}卡罗尔
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个给你  佩妮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one's for you, Penny
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.83,0:20:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买的充气船终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The raft I ordered has finally arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.97,0:21:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么海盗穿得好像邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are these pirates dressed like mail people?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们想偷邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They want to steal our mail
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驱逐入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Repel the boarders
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.70,0:21:21.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正在驱逐入侵者  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:21.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Repelling boarders, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.09,0:21:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harold
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送点货到付款
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm shipping these COD
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,货倒复垮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crash on delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空运要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here comes some air mail
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.22,0:21:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是海霸王的陪审团传票
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another jury summons for Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩垃圾邮件了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All we have left is junk mail
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.67,0:22:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进了邮局  他们绝对找不到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll never find us in this post office
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:16.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1124,164)}邮局
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:23.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986,312)}裤头村监狱
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.31,0:22:26.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天的邮件来了  狱长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:26.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's today's mail, warden
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.72,0:22:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery
